            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296007",
        "quote": "Our mandate expects that we will build on the Joint Inquiry's investigation and we will not be re-inventing the wheel. But we go to places which the Joint Inquiry was not permitted to explore.",
