        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296008",
        "quote": "And it turned out that the Roberts Commission did not fully utilize the information available and that it came to conclusions which were I think quite short sighted and, indeed, in some cases, scapegoated individuals.",
