    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296013",
        "quote": "Were there contacts over time between Iraq and al-Qaeda? Yes, there were efforts made to communicate. We found no evidence of collaboration in any effort to mount any kind of operation against the United States' interests.",
