    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296015",
        "quote": "But as I said to Dr. Rice following her testimony, and I think she appreciated it, we had our job to do and we did it best we could, trying to get answers to the important questions that the 9/11 Commission must answer.",
