    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296016",
        "quote": "Well, our position, and our chairman has talked about this extensively, is that we had a lot of intelligence prior to 9/11. We knew that two al Qaeda operatives who ultimately participated in the 9/11 disaster were in the United States. We didn't find them.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richard Ben-Veniste",
            "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296016"
