                "url": "/topics/had"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296017",
        "quote": "So we knew their intentions were to strike in the United States. We also knew from other sources of dozens of examples of where the notion of using planes as weapons was discussed.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richard Ben-Veniste",
            "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296017"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "United States",
