                "url": "/topics/dozens"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_296018",
        "quote": "The real question was, here we had this information, Bin Laden intends to strike in the United States. We knew they had struck before in 1993 at the World Trade Center in the first bombing of the trade center.",
