    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_677101",
        "quote": "When Richard M. Nixon resigned and Ford became the 38th president of the United States, the Watergate Special Prosecutor's Office, of which I was a member, was preparing for the criminal trials of Nixon's top aides - H.R. Haldeman, John Ehrlichman and John Mitchell.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richard Ben-Veniste",
            "url": "/quotes/richard_benveniste_677101"
